Class DataResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.DataResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Location, PointOfInterest, TileResource, WeatherResource

    public abstract class DataResource
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Least common denominator of all resources in GAIA. Each data resource is extending this class.
    Author:
    Johannes Bauer (Spezifikation: Matthias Fisch)
